## 🚀 How to Use

1. **Clone or Download the Project**:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-repo-name/responsive-portfolio-card.git
   ```

2. **Open the HTML File**:
   - Navigate to the project folder and open `index.html` in your favorite browser.

